title: Bug 9654: Modify Parameters: Dialog details
description:
The bug report mentions several issues with the dialog details in the 'Modify Parameters' functionality. The details are as follows:
 - Duplicated name validation could be performed on the first page.
 - The first and second column could be merged.

The bug report is lacking sufficient information in the OB (Observed Behavior), EB (Expected Behavior), and SR (Steps to Reproduce) sections. Hence, these sections need to be inferred and supplemented to provide a clear and complete bug report.
